data.description: Discover the perfect canvas for your dream home at 305 Chaplin Circle in beautiful Lompoc, CA. This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a unique opportunity for customization, with the master bathroom awaiting your personal touch. With 1,461 square feet of living space and a generous 8,712 square foot lot, there's plenty of room to create your ideal oasis.Enjoy the convenience of a recently updated kitchen, hallway bathroom, and laundry room, all completed in 2020. The possibilities are endless in this inviting home. Don't miss your chance to make it your own!
